OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FA mother whose baby died at Worthing
OL,8,FHospital says the NHS Trust let her
OL,9,Fdown when she needed them the most.
OL,11,FLiz Charton from Shoreham in West
OL,12,FSussex was left unmonitored for long
OL,13,Fperiods - despite a history of
OL,14,Fprevious complications with her
OL,15,Fpregnancies.
OL,17,FHer daughter, Hazel, died shortly
OL,18,Fafter being born on 14 July 2021.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FLiz is part of a bereaved families
OL,8,Fgroup meeting Health Secretary Wes
OL,9,FStreeting on Wednesday, pushing for a
OL,10,Ffull investigation into University
OL,11,FHospitals Sussex NHS Foundation Trust
OL,12,Fto be led by senior midwife and
OL,13,Finvestigator Donna Ockenden.
OL,15,FMs Charlton was admitted to Worthing
OL,16,FHospital in severe pain and blacking
OL,17,Fout at 28 weeks pregnant.
OL,19,FShe'd previously had six miscarriages
OL,20,Fand an ectopic pregnancy before her
OL,21,Fpregnancy with Hazel.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,F"I fought for my own pregnancy,
OL,8,Fadvocated, to be ignored, not heard,
OL,9,Fargued with, to get to the point where
OL,10,FI needed them the most, for them to
OL,11,Flet me down," she said.
OL,13,F"In my mind, with my complex history,
OL,14,FI should have been a high-risk case...
OL,15,Fand it never felt like my individual
OL,16,Fneeds were recognised.
OL,18,F"We're nearly half-a-decade on, and
OL,19,Fthere are still failings."
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FShe said she believed there were still
OL,8,Favoidable deaths happening at the
OL,9,Ftrust and that "change needs to happen
OL,10,Fnow".
OL,12,FMs Charlton is calling for
OL,13,Faccountability through an opt-out
OL,14,Findependent review by Ms Ockenden.
OL,16,F"The only way you can have clear
OL,17,Fchange is to have the most efficient,
OL,18,Feffective review done by someone that
OL,19,Fhas an evidence base of doing it, that
OL,20,Fknows how to do it, that's done it
OL,21,Fwell before," she said."
OL,26,@qD@POUrD@DO]xD@AOU}D@MO]}D@XOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FSo for me, it will give me
OL,8,Faccountability and justice, I think,
OL,9,Fand overall really change for the
OL,10,Ffuture.
OL,12,F"That's all I've ever wanted from the
OL,13,Fbeginning, is that this to never
OL,14,Fhappen to anyone else, for there to be
OL,15,Fsafe, maternity care for everyone."
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/15
