FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FThe clinical manager for dental
OL,8,Fpractices is part of the Sussex Truth
OL,9,Ffor Our Babies group calling for the
OL,10,Freview - she said that families were
OL,11,Fstill approaching the group each month
OL,12,Fbecause they believed their babies'
OL,13,Fdeaths were avoidable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FDuring her own pregnancy with Hazel,
OL,8,FMs Charlton said she found she was
OL,9,Frepeating crucial information around
OL,10,Fher medical history to new staff at
OL,11,Fappointments, including having a
OL,12,Futerine perforation which can increase
OL,13,Fthe risk of rupture in future
OL,14,Fpregnancies.
OL,16,FThen, on the evening of July 13 2021,
OL,17,Fat around 10.30pm, Ms Charlton became
OL,18,Funwell at home with severe pain,
OL,19,Fvomiting and blacking out.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FHer husband called an ambulance which
OL,8,Fthen took an hour before arriving at
OL,9,FWorthing Hospital, where she was
OL,10,Fadmitted at 1.30am on July 14 and her
OL,11,Fcondition deteriorated over several
OL,12,Fhours.
OL,14,FShe was not given pain relief, had a
OL,15,Fseizure trying to reach the toilet and
OL,16,Fwas supposed to have blood taken which
OL,17,Fnever happened, Ms Charlton said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FJust after 9am, Ms Charlton was put
OL,8,Funder general anaesthetic and despite
OL,9,Fefforts to resuscitate Hazel, she was
OL,10,Fstillborn and pronounced dead at
OL,11,F9.18am.
OL,13,FMs Charlton was still in surgery until
OL,14,Fmidday with a uterine rupture and in a
OL,15,Fcoma for a day.
OL,17,F"I was woken up that evening, I was in
OL,18,FITU and I knew Hazel had gone," she
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FMs Charlton said her and her husband
OL,8,FAnthony were a team, who honoured
OL,9,FHazel in everything they did and had a
OL,10,Fmemory box of her which included scan
OL,11,Fphotos, handprints, a blanket knitted
OL,12,Ffor her, a teddy and a clip of her
OL,13,Fhair.
OL,15,F"Hazel was the child that we prayed to
OL,16,FGod for. She was a gift, and I needed
OL,17,Fthem, the trust, the most then, and
OL,18,Fthey let me down," she said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,F"All our fears came true, our worst
OL,8,Fnightmares came true, and we live that
OL,9,Fevery day. We live what we feared the
OL,10,Fmost.
OL,12,F"I fought fearlessly to be heard, and
OL,13,FI'm still sat here with my arms empty."
OL,15,FAhead of the meeting with the Health
OL,16,FSecretary in Brighton, the Sussex
OL,17,FTruth for Our Babies group said Ms
OL,18,FCharlton's experiences showed why
OL,19,FSussex needed a "full and wide-
OL,20,Freaching" independent review.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUuD@gO]{D@QOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FThey said she was one of more than 60
OL,8,Ffamilies in the region who had been
OL,9,Faffected by maternity care failings.
OL,11,F"We are now putting our faith in Wes
OL,12,FStreeting to respond to our calls for
OL,13,Faccountability and change," the group
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FMs Charlton added: "The Secretary of
OL,17,FState should be fighting for us. We
OL,18,Fwill fight until we get what we need."
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@[O]xD@TOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FWorthing Hospital's maternity services
OL,8,Fwere upgraded by the Care Quality
OL,9,FCommission from "requires improvement"
OL,10,Fto "good" in February this year, while
OL,11,Fthe trust said it had increased
OL,12,Fstaffing levels, theatre capacity and
OL,13,Ftelephone triage in recent years.
OL,15,FDr Maggie Davies, chief nurse at
OL,16,FUniversity Hospitals Sussex NHS
OL,17,FFoundation Trust, said: "The loss of a
OL,18,Fbaby is an unimaginable tragedy for
OL,19,Fany parent, and we offer our deepest
OL,20,Fcondolences and sincere apologies to
OL,21,FHazel's family.
OL,26,@qD@QOUqD@fO]rD@DOUrD@IO]yD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776246948
OL,3,CBereaved mother says change still
OL,4,Cneeded at hospital trust where baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,F"Everyone involved in Hazel's care has
OL,8,Fbeen deeply affected by her loss, and
OL,9,Fthe suffering we know it has caused.
OL,11,F"We cannot comment further while legal
OL,12,Fproceedings are ongoing, but we
OL,13,Frecognise that no settlement can ever
OL,14,Ftruly compensate for the family's
OL,15,Fdistress.
OL,17,F"Our priority is always to provide the
OL,18,Fbest care ` that means listening
OL,19,Fcarefully, learning, and making
OL,20,Fchanges so that families today get the
OL,21,Fsafest care possible."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/15
